body.p: The Aggregated Cuneiform Resource Lookup was created by Øyvind Bjøru.

div.div:
Search for a sign value, e.g., šu, dam2, ha5, 'a4, or unugx.
The values are pulled from the Oracc Sign List.

div.p:
The cuneiform fonts needed to display the signs can be found here.
The proto-cuneiform signs are made available through CDLI.
The palaeographic section displays the data from the defunct Cuneiform Digital Palaeography Project, which is available here.
